<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 04:08:33 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列新的政治秩序将从 10 月 7 日崩溃的深渊中崛起</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/from-the-abyss-of-the-october-7-debacle-a-new-israeli-political-order-will-rise/0000018b-9b89-dbad-abfb-dbdd02fd0000</link><description>与赎罪日战争引发的政治转变类似，10 月 7 日将宣告利库德集团长期统治的结束。以色列新政府中不会有极端分子的地位</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 03:57:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/from-the-abyss-of-the-october-7-debacle-a-new-israeli-political-order-will-rise/0000018b-9b89-dbad-abfb-dbdd02fd0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管以色列猛烈袭击，哈马斯领导层仍保持对加沙的控制</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/despite-israels-fierce-attacks-hamas-leadership-maintains-control-on-gaza/0000018b-9c11-d27d-a9fb-deb916c20000</link><description>随着加沙战事愈演愈烈，以色列国防军的重点必须是拆除哈马斯地道。 ■ 人们可以感觉到美国对以色列的耐心正在减弱，因为国务卿布林肯呼吁允许增加对加沙的援助，并指出暂停战斗将导致美国对以色列的耐心逐渐减弱。帮助释放人质</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 03:56:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/despite-israels-fierce-attacks-hamas-leadership-maintains-control-on-gaza/0000018b-9c11-d27d-a9fb-deb916c20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府温柔地呼吁对加沙进行种族清洗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-govt-tender-souls-who-call-for-an-ethnic-cleansing-in-gaza/0000018b-9c0e-db71-a7df-fdcfbde20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 01:04:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-govt-tender-souls-who-call-for-an-ethnic-cleansing-in-gaza/0000018b-9c0e-db71-a7df-fdcfbde20000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-05/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-9c8f-db71-a7df-fdcfb98c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 23:05:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-05/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-9c8f-db71-a7df-fdcfb98c0000</guid></item><item><title>如果我们看不到加沙死去儿童的眼睛，我们还能看到儿童吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/if-we-cant-see-gazas-dead-childrens-eyes-can-we-see-children-at-all/0000018b-9c0e-d27d-a9fb-deafbc410000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 22:47:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/if-we-cant-see-gazas-dead-childrens-eyes-can-we-see-children-at-all/0000018b-9c0e-d27d-a9fb-deafbc410000</guid></item><item><title>以色列不得撤销其公民身份</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-05/ty-article/israel-must-not-revoke-their-citizenship/0000018b-9c0e-d27d-a9fb-deafbc650000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 22:11:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-05/ty-article/israel-must-not-revoke-their-citizenship/0000018b-9c0e-d27d-a9fb-deafbc650000</guid></item><item><title>纳斯鲁拉的讲话巩固了伊朗的地区地位，暗示有关加沙的最后一句话尚未说出口</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/nasrallahs-speech-cements-irans-regional-status-hints-last-word-on-gaza-not-said/0000018b-9c11-dbad-abfb-dddd1a380000</link><description>在媒体主导一周的“纳斯鲁拉节”结束后，他讲话的真实解读将通过他的具体行动揭晓。他澄清说，“所有选择都摆在桌面上”，并暗示真主党对加沙战争反应的最终决定主要取决于以色列在黎巴嫩的行动</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 21:53:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/nasrallahs-speech-cements-irans-regional-status-hints-last-word-on-gaza-not-said/0000018b-9c11-dbad-abfb-dddd1a380000</guid></item><item><title>以色列首次使用“箭3”火箭弹挫败加沙火箭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-thwarts-gaza-rocket-using-arrow-3-for-first-time/0000018b-9be7-d27d-a9fb-dbeff5a70000</link><description>这枚名为“Ayyash 250”的火箭是哈马斯拥有的最大火箭，在以色列最南端的阿拉瓦地区发射，是哈马斯有史以来发射距离最远的火箭</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 20:25:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-thwarts-gaza-rocket-using-arrow-3-for-first-time/0000018b-9be7-d27d-a9fb-dbeff5a70000</guid></item><item><title>犹太妇女在法国被刺伤，门上涂有纳粹十字记号；警方怀疑反犹太主义动机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-04/ty-article/french-police-hunt-suspect-in-stabbing-of-jewish-woman/0000018b-9bbd-d8a6-a38b-dfffed3a0000</link><description>受害者里昂的家中发现了纳粹十字记号涂鸦 ■ 警方将袭击视为谋杀未遂，可能有反犹太动机 ■ 法国内政部长：自哈马斯袭击以来，法国发生了 857 起反犹太行为</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 19:09:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-04/ty-article/french-police-hunt-suspect-in-stabbing-of-jewish-woman/0000018b-9bbd-d8a6-a38b-dfffed3a0000</guid></item><item><title>美国和阿拉伯伙伴对于以色列-加沙战争中停火的必要性存在分歧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/u-s-and-arab-partners-disagree-over-need-for-ceasefire-amid-israel-gaza-war/0000018b-9b55-d8a6-a38b-dfd704630000</link><description>布林肯表示“停火只会让哈马斯继续存在”，重点是增加人道主义援助并使以色列能够实现击败哈马斯的目标</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 18:14:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/u-s-and-arab-partners-disagree-over-need-for-ceasefire-amid-israel-gaza-war/0000018b-9b55-d8a6-a38b-dfd704630000</guid></item><item><title>数千人抗议席卷以色列各地，要求释放加沙地带被扣押的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/rallies-calling-for-the-release-of-the-hostages-held-in-gaza-sweeping-across-israel/0000018b-9b32-d27d-a9fb-dbbbb0640000</link><description>一些家庭成员一直睡在特拉维夫国防总部前的帐篷里，并表示他们打算一直睡到人质获释为止。人质亲属称“我责怪内塔尼亚胡”</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 17:10:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/rallies-calling-for-the-release-of-the-hostages-held-in-gaza-sweeping-across-israel/0000018b-9b32-d27d-a9fb-dbbbb0640000</guid></item><item><title>纳斯鲁拉表示，他不会为了加沙而牺牲黎巴嫩，让哈马斯自生自灭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/nasrallah-says-he-wont-sacrifice-lebanon-for-gaza-leaving-hamas-to-fend-for-itself/0000018b-9ad9-db71-a7df-ffdd53e10000</link><description>尽管地区盟友抱有期望，但真主党领导人明确表示，除非以色列深入黎巴嫩境内发动袭击或严重伤害平民，否则他不会发动全面战争</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 16:10:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/nasrallah-says-he-wont-sacrifice-lebanon-for-gaza-leaving-hamas-to-fend-for-itself/0000018b-9ad9-db71-a7df-ffdd53e10000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其召回驻以色列大使进行磋商；埃尔多安“抹掉”内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/turkey-recalls-ambassador-to-israel-for-consultations-erdogan-erases-netanyahu/0000018b-9ad4-d27d-a9fb-dafd2f710000</link><description>土耳其总统埃尔多安还表示，以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡不能再被视为土耳其的对手：“我们已经消灭了他”</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 15:48:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/turkey-recalls-ambassador-to-israel-for-consultations-erdogan-erases-netanyahu/0000018b-9ad4-d27d-a9fb-dafd2f710000</guid></item><item><title>当我们躲在安全室时，这些英雄出去拯救我们的基布兹——却再也没有回来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-we-hid-in-our-safe-room-these-heroes-went-out-to-save-our-kibbutz-and-never-returned/0000018b-9186-d7a8-afcf-bba7a2e30000</link><description>一名基布兹安全协调员在一名男孩被枪杀前救了他；一名边防警察士兵在他周围发现了五具恐怖分子的尸体；三名突击队员有时间一起拍了最后一张照片；两名巡逻士兵活着离开基布兹，但仍活着。上周在加沙陷落。纳哈奥兹英雄的生与死</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 14:30:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-we-hid-in-our-safe-room-these-heroes-went-out-to-save-our-kibbutz-and-never-returned/0000018b-9186-d7a8-afcf-bba7a2e30000</guid></item><item><title>美国官员称，哈马斯试图将其武装人员带着伤员和外国人偷偷带出加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/u-s-official-hamas-tried-to-sneak-out-fighters-with-wounded-and-foreign-nationals/0000018b-9a03-db71-a7df-ffcf50a00000</link><description>美国和埃及官员发现，被选中通过拉法过境点离开加沙进入埃及的人中，有三分之一是哈马斯战士，但最终撤离的 76 名受伤巴勒斯坦人中没有一人。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 11:25:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/u-s-official-hamas-tried-to-sneak-out-fighters-with-wounded-and-foreign-nationals/0000018b-9a03-db71-a7df-ffcf50a00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队公布了在加沙地带战斗中丧生的四名士兵的姓名；火箭击中以色列南部斯德洛特的家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article-live/u-s-official-hamas-tried-to-sneak-fighters-out-of-gaza-rockets-fired-at-central-israel/0000018b-9859-dbad-abfb-d9dda8850000</link><description>加沙边境社区火箭警报响起 ■ 以色列国防军称部队正在加沙地带北部和南部行动 ■ 土耳其埃尔多安称他已经“消灭”了内塔尼亚胡 ■ 28 名以色列士兵和军官在加沙地面进攻中丧生 ■ 第三次访问以色列后，布林肯访问以色列约旦并将继续前往土耳其 ■ 242 名人质在加沙被扣押，40 人仍然失踪 ■ 至少 1,300 名平民和士兵在哈马斯大屠杀中丧生 ■ 哈马斯卫生部声称加沙有 9,000 多人丧生</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 05:04:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article-live/u-s-official-hamas-tried-to-sneak-fighters-out-of-gaza-rockets-fired-at-central-israel/0000018b-9859-dbad-abfb-d9dda8850000</guid></item><item><title>在美国的支持下，以色列和乌克兰讨论泽伦斯基访问的可能性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/with-u-s-backing-israel-and-ukraine-discuss-possible-zelenskyy-visit/0000018b-9889-db71-a7df-fdcdae4b0000</link><description>讨论之际，拜登政府寻求建立亲美民主国家的统一战线，对抗俄罗斯-伊朗轴心</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 04:20:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/with-u-s-backing-israel-and-ukraine-discuss-possible-zelenskyy-visit/0000018b-9889-db71-a7df-fdcdae4b0000</guid></item><item><title>记者询问以色列警察为何袭击他。 “因为你说阿拉伯语，”他们回答道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-reporter-asked-why-israeli-cops-attacked-him-because-you-spoke-arabic-they-replied/0000018b-9774-d8a6-a38b-dff70b0f0000</link><description>安全官员一直在骚扰代表当地和外国媒体报道战争的以色列阿拉伯公民记者</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 00:20:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-reporter-asked-why-israeli-cops-attacked-him-because-you-spoke-arabic-they-replied/0000018b-9774-d8a6-a38b-dff70b0f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡应该为 10 月 7 日的失败负责吗？这些利库德集团选民宁愿相信阴谋论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/bibis-to-blame-for-oct-7-failures-likud-voters-prefer-to-believe-conspiracy-theories/0000018b-90c2-d477-a1ff-f7c2b8d10000</link><description>利库德集团在民调中的支持率大幅下滑，广大公众对政府感到愤怒。但对该党的一些传统据点的（有点危险的）访问揭示了为什么有些人仍然支持内塔尼亚胡——即使是现在</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 23:09:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/bibis-to-blame-for-oct-7-failures-likud-voters-prefer-to-believe-conspiracy-theories/0000018b-90c2-d477-a1ff-f7c2b8d10000</guid></item><item><title>大卫·彼得雷乌斯将军向以色列发出警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/gen-david-petraeus-has-a-warning-for-israel/0000018b-96c9-db7e-af9b-ffcb0e090000</link><description>在这些战争期间指挥美国陆军的戴维·彼得雷乌斯将军表示，当以色列陷入加沙“异常艰难”的战场时，以色列军队必须从美国打击基地组织和伊斯兰国的痛苦经历中吸取教训</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 20:59:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/gen-david-petraeus-has-a-warning-for-israel/0000018b-96c9-db7e-af9b-ffcb0e090000</guid></item></channel></rss>